name: Sausage Quiche Squares
ingredients: 1 pound pork sausage, browned and drained
1/2 cup onion, chopped, 2.5 ounces or 1 small

instructions.en: Spread browned and drained sausage in a greased 9x13" baking dish.
instructions.sk: Rozložte opečenú a odkvapkanú klobásu do vymastenej 23x33 cm zapekacej formy.
instructions.ja: 油を塗った9x13インチの焼き皿に炒めて油を切ったソーセージを広げます。

instructions.en: Layer with half of the cheese, then onion, chiles, jalapeños, and remaining cheese.
instructions.sk: Vrstvite polovicou syra, potom cibuľou, čili papričkami, jalapeños a zvyšným syrom.
instructions.ja: チーズの半分を敷き、その上に玉ねぎ、チリ、ハラペーニョ、残りのチーズを重ねます。

instructions.en: Beat eggs with seasonings (chili powder, cumin, salt, garlic powder, pepper).
instructions.sk: Vyšľahajte vajcia s korením (čili prášok, rasca, soľ, cesnakový prášok, korenie).
instructions.ja: 卵と調味料（チリパウダー、クミン、塩、ガーリックパウダー、コショウ）を混ぜます。

instructions.en: Pour egg mixture evenly over everything.
instructions.sk: Nalejte vaječnú zmes rovnomerne na všetko.
instructions.ja: 卵液を全体に均等にかけます。
切る前に10分間置きます。
